   <note type="contents">7. fol. 95a-169a: Tadhkirah / Muḥammad Jaʻfar Jāblāqī (fl. 1811)</note>
   <note type="contents">8. fol. 169b-170b: [Blank]</note>
   <note type="contents">9. fol. 171a-176b: [Taʻlīq ʻalá mabḥath al-zawāl min Sharḥ al-Lumʻah al-Dimashqīyah] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">10. fol. 176b-181a: Rasāʼil fī al-mawāzin / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">11. fol. 181a-182b: [Risālah fī masʼalat wujūb al-mahr ʻinda mawt al-zawj aw al-zawjah qabl al-dukhūl] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718
      or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">12. fol. 182b-183b: [Risālah fī masʼalat al-mahr] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">13. fol. 183b-188b: [Risālah fī al-daʻwā ʻalá al-mayyit] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">14. fol. 188b-189a: [Kitāb al-Saʻādāt. Selections] / Jaʻfar al-Ṣādiq (d. 765 or 6)</note>
   <note type="contents">15. fol. 189a-191a: Risālah fī ṣiḥḥat al-ṣulḥ ʻalá al-majhūl / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">16. fol. 191b-195b: Risālah fī ghusālat al-najāsah / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">17. fol. 195b-204a: Risālah fī anna al-insān baʻd al-mawt ḥayy ḥaqīqatan / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">18. fol. 204a-209a: Masʼalat tajwīz al-ʻudūl min kull sūrah ʻalá al-jaḥd / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">19. fol. 209a-221b: [Risālah fī ajwibat thalāth masāʼil Nāṣir ibn Muḥammad al-Jārūdī] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">20. fol. 221b-231a: Masāʼil tataʻallaqu bi-al-ʻiṭārah bal bi-muṭlaq al-tijārah [al-Risālah al-ʻAṭṭārīyah] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr]
