   <note type="contents">21. fol. 231a-237b: Hal al-ṭalqah wa-al-ṭalqatayn tabqá bi-al-taḥlīl aw tanhadam / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">22. fol. 237b-239b: [Ajwibat masāʼil Yaḥyá ibn Ḥusayn al-Ahsāʼī] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">23. fol. 239b-244b: [Risālah fī al-najāsah] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">24. fol. 245a-248a: [Ajwibat masāʼil ʻAbd al-Imām al-Aḥsāʼī] / Aḥmad ibn Ibrāhīm al-Baḥrānī [Ibn ʻUṣfūr] (d. 1718 or 19)</note>
   <note type="contents">25. fol. 249a-292b: al-Durrah / Muḥammad Mahdī Ṭabāṭabāʼī, Baḥr al-ʻUlūm (d. 1797 or 8)</note>
